{"tid":2211083,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"匯控中止7連跌 留意購證20212","createTime":"2020-09-21T01:57:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-21T02:06:21.000Z","uid":219470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d90a05cf4fec419b01c664b843b673296767f342","tid":2211083,"uid":219470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T01:57:34.000Z","msg":"匯豐控股（0005）七連跌後，終於止跌回穩，曾反彈逾1%至31元以上，收市仍保持升勢。跌勢略見喘定後，向上觀望重上33元的機會，30元關口或仍具支持。觀望反彈持續，看好可考慮匯豐認購證20212，行使價35.28元，2021年02月到期，實際槓桿約8.6倍。憂慮再遇跌勢，看淡可考慮匯豐認沽證23926，行使價25.95元，2021年02月到期，實際槓桿約6.1倍。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F/article/20200921/s00004/1600625840216/%E4%BD%95%E5%95%9F%E8%81%B0-%E5%8C%AF%E6%8E%A7%E4%B8%AD%E6%AD%A27%E9%80%A3%E8%B7%8C-%E7%95%99%E6%84%8F%E8%B3%BC%E8%AD%8920212\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25BF%259F%2Farticle%2F20200921%2Fs00004%2F1600625840216%2F%25E4%25BD%2595%25E5%2595%259F%25E8%2581%25B0-%25E5%258C%25AF%25E6%258E%25A7%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%25AD%25A27%25E9%2580%25A3%25E8%25B7%258C-%25E7%2595%2599%25E6%2584%258F%25E8%25B3%25BC%25E8%25AD%258920212&d=nIll2RoSQXmni3IMQi%2BZopS3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=1c6b96b3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25BF%259F%2Farticle%2F20200921%2Fs00004%2F1600625840216%2F%25E4%25BD%2595%25E5%2595%259F%25E8%2581%25B0-%25E5%258C%25AF%25E6%258E%25A7%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%25AD%25A27%25E9%2580%25A3%25E8%25B7%258C-%25E7%2595%2599%25E6%2584%258F%25E8%25B3%25BC%25E8%25AD%258920212&h=ab7dd028\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F/article/20200921/s00004/1600625840216/%E4%BD%95%E5%95%9F%E8%81%B0-%E5%8C%AF%E6%8E%A7%E4%B8%AD%E6%AD%A27%E9%80%A3%E8%B7%8C-%E7%95%99%E6%84%8F%E8%B3%BC%E8%AD%8920212</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asset